{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">1.知道酸或碱能使指示剂变色；</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">2.掌握酚酞在不同酸碱性下的颜色。</span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">在酸性和中性条件下酚酞为无色，碱性为红色。</span></p>"},{"title":"用品","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">仪器：试管、试管架。</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">药品：氢氧化钠溶液、氢氧化钙溶液、稀盐酸、稀醋酸、酚酞。</span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">在四支试管中分别加入氢氧化钠溶液、氢氧化钙溶液、稀盐酸和稀醋酸，然后分别滴加酚酞，观察实验现象。</span></p>"},{"title":"现象","data":"<table border=\"1\" style=\"width:500px\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">溶液</span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">加入酚酞后的颜色</span></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">氢氧化钙溶液</span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">红色</span></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">氢氧化钠溶液</span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">红色</span></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">稀盐酸</span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">无色</span></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">稀醋酸</span></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">无色</span></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}